description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Squat + Plyometric Circuit ' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

Original workout description: Total body focus off Hydrow with dumbbells and 2-minute intervals on Hydrow.

Max rhythm: 24, Format: AMRAP...
